WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:01.000
 PREVIOUSLY ON "DEXTER"...

2
00:00:02.133 --> 00:00:05.067
Dexter: NO BLOOD.
 WHAT A GORGEOUS IDEA.

3
00:00:05.133 --> 00:00:09.701
REFRIGERATED TRUCK.
HE WANTS A COLD ENVIRONMENT...

4
00:00:09.767 --> 00:00:11.100
TO SLOW THE FLOW OF BLOOD.

5
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:13.200
[ GASPS ]

6
00:00:13.267 --> 00:00:15.501
 I SUPPOSE I SHOULD BE UPSET.
 BUT I'M NOT.

7
00:00:15.567 --> 00:00:17.767
 IN FACT. I THINK
 THIS IS A FRIENDLY MESSAGE.

8
00:00:17.834 --> 00:00:20.901
 KIND OF LIKE.
 "HEY. WANT TO PLAY?"

9
00:00:22.634 --> 00:00:24.400
KARA. IT'S ME.
IT'S JAMES.

10
00:00:24.467 --> 00:00:27.834
YOU JUST OPENED
A DANGEROUS DOOR.

11
00:00:27.901 --> 00:00:29.567
NO. MAN.
YOU DID...

12
00:00:29.634 --> 00:00:32.767
WHEN YOU MURDERED A COP
AND AN INNOCENT LADY.

13
00:00:32.834 --> 00:00:36.367
WAS KARA SLEEPING WITH SOMEONE
OTHER THAN RICKY?

14
00:00:36.434 --> 00:00:37.634
WAS IT YOU?

15
00:00:37.701 --> 00:00:39.267
[ SCOFFS ]

16
00:00:39.334 --> 00:00:41.234
WHAT THE FUCK
WERE YOU THINKING?

17
00:00:41.300 --> 00:00:43.801
GOING OUT TONIGHT WITH THE GUYS.
BLOW OFF STEAM. YOU IN?

18
00:00:43.868 --> 00:00:45.067
HEY. MAN.
SOUNDS GOOD.

19
00:00:45.133 --> 00:00:47.901
I THOUGHT YOU SAID YOU WANTED
TO GO GET SHIT-FACED.

20
00:00:47.968 --> 00:00:49.701
I AM SHIT-FACED.

21
00:00:49.767 --> 00:00:51.901
I SHOWED MY FACE TO GUERRERO.
HIS WHOLE CHURCH.

22
00:00:51.968 --> 00:00:54.601
THEY'RE GONNA THINK
I'M BEHIND THIS SHIT.

23
00:00:54.667 --> 00:00:57.767
YOU FUCKED MY SISTER.
YOU FUCKED A COP'S WIFE.

24
00:00:57.834 --> 00:01:00.067
NOW YOU'RE JUST FUCKED.
BUDDY.

25
00:01:01.234 --> 00:01:03.667
Dexter:
HE'S ESCALATING THE THRILL.

26
00:01:03.734 --> 00:01:04.734
POSING HIS VICTIM

27
00:01:04.801 --> 00:01:06.901
IN THE MIDDLE
OF A 20.000-SEAT ARENA

28
00:01:06.968 --> 00:01:08.167
FOR ALL MIAMI TO SEE.

29
00:01:08.234 --> 00:01:10.300
TO SHOW US WHAT HE'S CAPABLE
OF DOING.

30
00:01:10.367 --> 00:01:11.334
WHAT DID I MISS?

31
00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:13.267
FINGERTIPS.

32
00:01:13.334 --> 00:01:15.167
FUCKIN'-A.
THAT'S MY GIRL.

33
00:01:15.234 --> 00:01:17.767
THIS BODY BELONGS TO THE FROZEN
FINGERTIPS IN THE TRUCK.

34
00:01:17.834 --> 00:01:19.868
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN.

35
00:01:19.934 --> 00:01:22.901
I GIVE YOU TONY TUCCI.
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

36
00:01:22.968 --> 00:01:24.267
BULLSHIT.

37
00:01:24.334 --> 00:01:25.934
 OF COURSE
 I AGREE WITH MY SISTER.

38
00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:28.534
 BUT UNLIKE HER. I'M NOT UPSET.

39
00:01:28.601 --> 00:01:31.434
 HE'S STILL OUT THERE.
 AND I'M WAITING...

40
00:01:31.501 --> 00:01:33.501
 BREATHLESS.

41
00:03:36.834 --> 00:03:38.334
 I FIND PEOPLE AROUND ME

42
00:03:38.400 --> 00:03:41.133
 ARE ALL MAKING
 SOME KIND OF CONNECTION.

43
00:03:41.200 --> 00:03:42.801
 LIKE FRIENDSHIP OR ROMANCE.

44
00:03:42.868 --> 00:03:45.934
 BUT HUMAN BONDS ALWAYS
 LEAD TO MESSY COMPLICATIONS --

45
00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:51.200
 COMMITMENT. SHARING.
 DRIVING PEOPLE TO THE AIRPORT.

46
00:03:51.267 --> 00:03:53.667
 BESIDES. IF I LET SOMEONE
 GET THAT CLOSE.

47
00:03:53.734 --> 00:03:56.367
 THEY'D SEE
 WHO I REALLY AM...

48
00:03:56.434 --> 00:03:58.000
 AND I CAN'T LET THAT
 HAPPEN.

49
00:03:58.067 --> 00:04:02.701
 SO...TIME TO PUT ON MY MASK.

50
00:04:05.734 --> 00:04:07.834
I NEED
YOUR EXPERTISE.

51
00:04:07.901 --> 00:04:09.434
I LIVE TO SERVE.

52
00:04:09.501 --> 00:04:11.200
EXCUSE US. FELLAS.

53
00:04:15.200 --> 00:04:18.434
INTERESTING HAND JOB.

54
00:04:18.501 --> 00:04:20.701
THAT'S FUNNY.

55
00:04:20.767 --> 00:04:23.334
IT IS?

56
00:04:23.400 --> 00:04:26.067
SO. HOW LONG YOU THINK
IT'S BEEN THERE?

57
00:04:28.834 --> 00:04:32.634
THIS FEELS FAMILIAR.

58
00:04:32.701 --> 00:04:34.434
OKAY.

59
00:04:34.501 --> 00:04:36.167
SO. HOW LONG'S IT BEEN THERE?

60
00:04:38.100 --> 00:04:41.734
BLOOD STOPPED POOLING.
STILL WET...

61
00:04:41.801 --> 00:04:43.334
COUPLE HOURS AT THE MOST.

62
00:04:43.400 --> 00:04:44.834
WHAT TIME WAS IT FOUND?

63
00:04:44.901 --> 00:04:47.701
A JOGGER CALLED IT IN
THIS MORNING ABOUT 7:30.

64
00:04:47.767 --> 00:04:49.901
NO PRINTS.
WIPED CLEAN.

65
00:04:49.968 --> 00:04:51.667
REAL CREEP SHOW. HUH?

66
00:04:51.734 --> 00:04:53.934
ANY SIGN OF THE REST
OF THE BODY?

67
00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:55.434
JUST MR. HAND.

68
00:04:55.501 --> 00:04:58.200
DO YOU THINK THIS IS
OUR GUY'S WORK?

69
00:04:58.267 --> 00:05:01.133
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER?
IT'S HARD TO SAY.

70
00:05:01.200 --> 00:05:03.667
THERE'S BLOOD.
THAT'S DIFFERENT.

71
00:05:03.734 --> 00:05:07.167
PLUS. IT'S A MALE VICTIM --
HAVEN'T SEEN THAT BEFORE.

72
00:05:07.234 --> 00:05:09.901
THE CUT APPEARS TO BE
ALMOST DELICATE.

73
00:05:09.968 --> 00:05:13.467
YOU SEE BETWEEN THE FIRST
AND SECOND ROW OF CARPALS --

74
00:05:13.534 --> 00:05:17.200
VERY SURGICAL.

75
00:05:17.267 --> 00:05:20.934
CHECK OUT
WHAT ELSE HE LEFT BEHIND.

76
00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:25.133
A POSTCARD
TO REMEMBER HIM BY.

77
00:05:30.601 --> 00:05:33.033
HOW FAR IS RAND BEACH
FROM HERE?

78
00:05:33.100 --> 00:05:34.501
THIS IS RAND BEACH.

79
00:05:34.567 --> 00:05:37.801
IT WAS RENAMED PETRIE BEACH
A FEW YEARS AGO.

80
00:05:50.334 --> 00:05:51.901
Harry:
OKAY. EVERYBODY.

81
00:05:55.234 --> 00:05:59.167
EVERYBODY SAY "STINKY FEET."

82
00:05:59.234 --> 00:06:00.834
STINKY FEET!
STINKY FEET!
STINKY FEET!

83
00:06:00.901 --> 00:06:03.567
WAIT. NOBODY MOVE.
DEXTER. WERE YOU SMILING?

84
00:06:03.634 --> 00:06:04.834
NO.

85
00:06:04.901 --> 00:06:06.167
OKAY.
WE'LL DO ANOTHER ONE.

86
00:06:06.234 --> 00:06:08.100
THIS TIME. EVERYBODY SMILE.
YOU. TOO. DEX.

87
00:06:08.167 --> 00:06:09.701
YEAH. PRETEND
YOU'RE BURNING ANTS.

88
00:06:09.767 --> 00:06:10.968
SHUT YOUR DAMN FACE.
DEB.

89
00:06:11.033 --> 00:06:12.400
HEY. LANGUAGE. PLEASE.

90
00:06:12.467 --> 00:06:14.400
WHAT?
SHE ALWAYS TALKS LIKE THAT.

91
00:06:14.467 --> 00:06:16.501
ENOUGH. YOU TWO.
DEXTER. COME HERE.

92
00:06:22.634 --> 00:06:23.767
WHAT'S YOUR PROBLEM?

93
00:06:23.834 --> 00:06:25.167
I HATE THE BEACH.

94
00:06:25.234 --> 00:06:27.801
IT'S SANDY AND GROSS AND NASTY.
AND I WANT TO GO HOME.

95
00:06:27.868 --> 00:06:29.801
TOO BAD.
YOU'RE PART OF A FAMILY.

96
00:06:29.868 --> 00:06:33.501
AND BEING PART OF A FAMILY
MEANS SMILING FOR PHOTOS.

97
00:06:33.567 --> 00:06:37.267
WHY SHOULD I PRETEND
I'M HAPPY?

98
00:06:37.334 --> 00:06:39.968
BECAUSE IT'LL MAKE
YOUR MOM HAPPY.

99
00:06:40.033 --> 00:06:42.534
AND BECAUSE
IT'S HOW YOU FIT IN.

100
00:06:42.601 --> 00:06:45.000
REMEMBER WE TALKED
ABOUT THAT?

101
00:06:45.067 --> 00:06:46.100
YEAH.

102
00:06:46.167 --> 00:06:47.300
THIS IS HOW YOU DO IT.

103
00:06:47.367 --> 00:06:49.634
WHEN SOMEBODY TAKES
YOUR PICTURE. YOU SMILE.

104
00:06:49.701 --> 00:06:51.834
IT DOESN'T MATTER
IF YOU'RE HAPPY OR NOT.

105
00:06:51.901 --> 00:06:55.267
YOU JUST DO IT TO FIT IN.
OKAY?

106
00:06:55.334 --> 00:06:56.501
OKAY.

107
00:06:56.567 --> 00:06:59.300
ALL RIGHT.

108
00:06:59.367 --> 00:07:02.200
COME HERE. HANDSOME.

109
00:07:02.267 --> 00:07:04.667
OKAY.
EVERYBODY READY?

110
00:07:07.367 --> 00:07:09.534
ONE MORE TIME.

111
00:07:11.367 --> 00:07:13.000
STINKY FEET!
STINKY FEET!
STINKY FEET!

112
00:07:15.334 --> 00:07:19.267
YEAH. I JUST NEED TO STOP BY MY
APARTMENT TO PICK UP A FEW LABS.

113
00:07:19.334 --> 00:07:22.868
STRAIGHT TO THE STATION AFTER.
YEAH. THANKS. LIEUTENANT.

114
00:07:35.267 --> 00:07:39.801
 DEXTER MORGAN.
 THIS IS YOUR LIFE.

115
00:07:39.868 --> 00:07:43.501
 IT IS MY NEW FRIEND --
 THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

116
00:07:43.567 --> 00:07:46.033
 WHEN HE BROKE
 INTO MY APARTMENT.

117
00:07:46.100 --> 00:07:48.367
 HE TOOK SOME TIME
 TO GET TO KNOW ME --

118
00:07:48.434 --> 00:07:53.567
 MY LIFE...MY SECRETS.

119
00:08:03.834 --> 00:08:06.801
 ...HAVE EVEN BROUGHT IN
 MANPOWER FROM OTHER COUNTIES

120
00:08:06.868 --> 00:08:09.033
 IN AN EFFORT
 TO EXPEDITE THE SEARCH.

121
00:08:09.100 --> 00:08:12.434
 OFFICIALLY. MR. TUCCI HAS NOT
 BEEN CHARGED WITH ANY CRIME...

122
00:08:12.501 --> 00:08:15.400
THEN TELL THE FUCKING GOVERNOR
TO FREE UP FUNDS FOR OVERTIME.

123
00:08:15.467 --> 00:08:18.133
THE MORE GUYS I GOT OUT THERE.
THE SOONER WE FIND TUCCI.

124
00:08:18.200 --> 00:08:21.033
UH. KELLY.
I'LL GET BACK TO YOU.

125
00:08:21.100 --> 00:08:24.133
 ...IS STILL THE DEPARTMENT'S
 TOP PRIORITY.

126
00:08:24.200 --> 00:08:25.667
[ TV SHUTS OFF ]

127
00:08:25.734 --> 00:08:26.934
WHAT'S WRONG?

128
00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:29.734
FINGERPRINT I.D. CAME BACK
ON THAT HAND FROM THE BEACH.

129
00:08:29.801 --> 00:08:31.234
IT BELONGS
TO TONY TUCCI.

130
00:08:31.300 --> 00:08:34.300
YOUR ICE-TRUCK KILLER
SUSPECT.

131
00:08:34.367 --> 00:08:35.901
WHAT?

132
00:08:38.267 --> 00:08:40.367
WAIT A MINUTE.

133
00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:44.367
NO. NO. NO. NO.
NO WAY.

134
00:08:44.434 --> 00:08:46.634
NO WAY.

135
00:08:46.701 --> 00:08:49.868
I MEAN. THIS --
THIS HAS TO BE A MISTAKE.

136
00:08:49.934 --> 00:08:52.167
THE MISTAKE WAS UNLEASHING
A HIGH-PROFILE MANHUNT

137
00:08:52.234 --> 00:08:53.767
BEFORE YOU HAD
ALL THE FACTS.

138
00:08:57.067 --> 00:08:58.200
FUCK.

139
00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:03.334
OKAY.

140
00:09:03.400 --> 00:09:05.601
THIS DOESN'T MEAN
THAT TUCCI IS NOT THE KILLER.

141
00:09:05.667 --> 00:09:07.467
DON'T.

142
00:09:07.534 --> 00:09:10.100
JUST -- JUST DON'T.

143
00:09:10.167 --> 00:09:13.601
YOU WANTED TO BE ON TV --
WELL. GET READY...

144
00:09:13.667 --> 00:09:16.167
'CAUSE THE PRESS
WILL ANNIHILATE US FOR THIS.

145
00:09:16.234 --> 00:09:20.300
WE'LL BE LUCKY IF TUCCI'S MOTHER
DOESN'T FILE A LAWSUIT.

146
00:09:22.067 --> 00:09:24.434
ALL RIGHT.

147
00:09:24.501 --> 00:09:27.834
YOU GO TALK TO THAT WOMAN.
DO YOUR MEA CULPAS.

148
00:09:27.901 --> 00:09:29.200
IF WE HANDLE THIS RIGHT.

149
00:09:29.267 --> 00:09:32.067
MAYBE WE CAN MITIGATE
THE FALLOUT.

150
00:09:32.133 --> 00:09:34.734
TOM...

151
00:09:34.801 --> 00:09:37.067
I'M THE LAST PERSON
SHE WANTS TO SEE.

152
00:09:37.133 --> 00:09:38.834
I CALLED HER SON
A KILLER.

153
00:09:38.901 --> 00:09:41.133
AND NOW'S YOUR CHANCE
TO MAKE IT RIGHT.

154
00:09:45.634 --> 00:09:47.434
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

155
00:09:47.501 --> 00:09:49.334
[ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING ]

156
00:10:01.267 --> 00:10:03.167
LaGUERTA SCREWED THE POOCH
ON THIS ONE. HUH?

157
00:10:03.234 --> 00:10:04.434
I'M TAKING POINT.

158
00:10:04.501 --> 00:10:06.968
YOU CAN HELP BY GETTING
ALL NONESSENTIALS OFF THE BEACH.

159
00:10:07.033 --> 00:10:09.300
SECURE AND SEPARATE
ANY WITNESSES. ALL RIGHT?

160
00:10:09.367 --> 00:10:12.467
WILL DO.
WHAT DID THE CAPTAIN SAY?

161
00:10:12.534 --> 00:10:14.400
DID HE MAKE HER CRY?

162
00:10:18.467 --> 00:10:21.868
JUST CONTROL
THE FUCKING BEACH. ANGEL.

163
00:10:23.767 --> 00:10:25.701
I KNEW TUCCI WASN'T THE KILLER.
I KNEW IT.

164
00:10:25.767 --> 00:10:27.901
LaGUERTA WHIPPED UP A MANHUNT
FOR A RENT-A-COP.

165
00:10:27.968 --> 00:10:29.801
OH. MAN. I WISH
I COULD HAVE BEEN THERE

166
00:10:29.868 --> 00:10:31.601
TO SEE THE CAPTAIN RIP HER
A NEW ONE.

167
00:10:31.667 --> 00:10:32.901
MORGAN. CALM DOWN.

168
00:10:32.968 --> 00:10:35.200
LaGUERTA INSULTED
THE REAL KILLER'S INTELLIGENCE.

169
00:10:35.267 --> 00:10:36.801
AND NOW HE'S GETTING BACK
AT US

170
00:10:36.868 --> 00:10:38.434
FOR CHASING
AFTER THE WRONG GUY.

171
00:10:38.501 --> 00:10:40.968
YOU SEE ALL THESE PEOPLE
OVER HERE?
YEAH.

172
00:10:41.033 --> 00:10:43.467
WHAT ARE THEY?
UH. POTENTIAL WITNESSES.

173
00:10:43.534 --> 00:10:46.601
AND WHAT DO WE DO WITH
POTENTIAL WITNESSES. MORGAN?

174
00:10:46.667 --> 00:10:49.801
WE --
WE INTERVIEW THEM.

175
00:10:49.868 --> 00:10:52.133
GOT IT.

176
00:11:00.534 --> 00:11:03.400
WHERE IS HE...

177
00:11:03.467 --> 00:11:04.901
THE REST OF HIM?

178
00:11:08.868 --> 00:11:10.701
WE'RE --
WE'RE STILL LOOKING.

179
00:11:10.767 --> 00:11:13.934
THE ENTIRE FORCE IS LOOKING.
WE'RE MAKING EVERY EFFORT.

180
00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:17.167
ARE YOU SURE IT'S TONY?
BECAUSE...

181
00:11:17.234 --> 00:11:19.200
YES.

182
00:11:19.267 --> 00:11:22.367
I'M AFRAID SO.

183
00:11:22.434 --> 00:11:24.567
[ SNIFFLES ]

184
00:11:26.934 --> 00:11:28.501
MRS. TUCCI...

185
00:11:28.567 --> 00:11:32.534
I SAID SOME VERY HARSH THINGS
ABOUT YOUR SON.

186
00:11:32.601 --> 00:11:34.100
THANK YOU.

187
00:11:38.400 --> 00:11:40.300
"THANK YOU"?
FOR WHAT?

188
00:11:40.367 --> 00:11:43.601
FOR COMING TO TELL ME
IN PERSON.

189
00:11:43.667 --> 00:11:46.300
FOR GOD'S SAKE.
PLEASE.

190
00:11:46.367 --> 00:11:48.834
THERE'S NOTHING MORE IMPORTANT
THAN THIS.

191
00:11:48.901 --> 00:11:52.267
CAN YOU FIND
MY SON'S BODY?

192
00:11:52.334 --> 00:11:55.467
IF IT'S THE LAST THING
I DO.

193
00:11:55.534 --> 00:11:57.467
I MADE A GRAVE --

194
00:11:57.534 --> 00:12:00.434
BRING HIM HOME. PLEASE.

195
00:12:00.501 --> 00:12:02.868
I JUST WANT TO BURY MY SON.

196
00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:19.367
I DO LOVE HALLOWEEN.

197
00:12:19.434 --> 00:12:21.834
WHAT'S INSIDE OF A PUMPKIN?

198
00:12:21.901 --> 00:12:23.167
SEE FOR YOURSELF.

199
00:12:23.234 --> 00:12:24.334
EW!

200
00:12:24.400 --> 00:12:26.334
YOU DON'T LIKE THIS STUFF?
I DO.

201
00:12:26.400 --> 00:12:27.934
COME ON.
GET IN THERE.

202
00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:30.367
[ CHUCKLES ]

203
00:12:30.434 --> 00:12:33.467
I'LL FINISH CLEANING THIS OUT.
YOU CAN CARVE IT TOMORROW.

204
00:12:33.534 --> 00:12:35.667
[ DOG BARKING ]

205
00:12:35.734 --> 00:12:37.334
THERE HE IS AGAIN.
MOM.

206
00:12:37.400 --> 00:12:39.634
MY GOD.
IT'S EVERY NIGHT NOW.

207
00:12:39.701 --> 00:12:42.367
THAT DOG?
WHERE'S IT COMING FROM?

208
00:12:42.434 --> 00:12:43.901
NEXT DOOR --
MY NEIGHBOR'S.

209
00:12:43.968 --> 00:12:46.667
LEAVES THE POOR THING
IN THE YARD ALL DAY AND NIGHT.

210
00:12:46.734 --> 00:12:48.000
IT'S BEEN GETTING WORSE.

211
00:12:48.067 --> 00:12:49.667
I MEAN.
I WOULD TALK TO HER.

212
00:12:49.734 --> 00:12:51.701
BUT I DON'T WANT
TO START SOMETHING.

213
00:12:51.767 --> 00:12:55.501
LISTEN TO HIM. MOM.
HE'S SO SAD.

214
00:12:55.567 --> 00:12:58.334
I JUST WISH HE WOULD SHUT UP
SO I COULD SLEEP.

215
00:12:58.400 --> 00:13:00.067
DO YOU WANT ME
TO TALK TO HER?

216
00:13:00.133 --> 00:13:02.334
NO.
YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO THAT.

217
00:13:02.400 --> 00:13:05.100
[ BARKING CONTINUES ]

218
00:13:05.167 --> 00:13:07.501
I INSIST.

219
00:13:17.334 --> 00:13:19.467
[ CHUCKLING EVILLY ]

220
00:13:25.367 --> 00:13:28.434
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

221
00:13:30.234 --> 00:13:32.934
HELLO.
I DON'T THINK WE'VE MET.

222
00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:35.167
BOYFRIEND OF THE BLONDE
NEXT DOOR.

223
00:13:35.234 --> 00:13:36.534
I'VE SEEN YOU AROUND.

224
00:13:36.601 --> 00:13:38.567
LOOK. I'M JUST GETTING IN.
I'M TIRED.

225
00:13:38.634 --> 00:13:40.334
THAT'S PRECISELY
WHY I'M HERE.

226
00:13:40.400 --> 00:13:42.901
WE CAN'T HELP BUT NOTICE
YOUR DOG. UH. CRIES...

227
00:13:42.968 --> 00:13:44.100
A LOT.

228
00:13:44.167 --> 00:13:45.133
I KNOW.

229
00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:47.033
MY EX MOVED OUT
AND LEFT HIS DOG.

230
00:13:47.100 --> 00:13:48.300
OH.

231
00:13:48.367 --> 00:13:50.434
TRUST ME. I WISH
THERE WAS SOMETHING I COULD DO.

232
00:13:50.501 --> 00:13:54.067
YOU COULD. UH.
TAKE HIM INSIDE.

233
00:13:54.133 --> 00:13:55.634
WALTER'S AN OUTSIDE DOG.

234
00:13:55.701 --> 00:13:57.701
YOU PUT WALTER INSIDE.
WALTER'S AN INSIDE DOG.

235
00:13:57.767 --> 00:13:59.901
HE DOESN'T LIKE
BEING INSIDE.

236
00:13:59.968 --> 00:14:02.367
DID HE TELL YOU THAT?

237
00:14:02.434 --> 00:14:04.634
[ BARKING CONTINUES ]

238
00:14:06.701 --> 00:14:09.567
WE'D APPRECIATE IT IF YOU COULD
FIND A WAY TO KEEP HIM QUIET.

239
00:14:09.634 --> 00:14:10.934
THE KIDS ARE UPSET.

240
00:14:11.033 --> 00:14:13.701
MAYBE THAT'S 'CAUSE THEY THINK
THEIR CRACKHEAD FATHER

241
00:14:13.767 --> 00:14:16.167
IS GONNA COME BACK
AND BEAT THEIR ASSES AGAIN.

242
00:14:17.901 --> 00:14:20.667
YOU KNOW WHAT WORKS FOR ME?
EARPLUGS.

243
00:14:28.400 --> 00:14:30.634
[ CHUCKLING EVILLY ]

244
00:14:30.701 --> 00:14:35.501
Dexter: I COULD MAKE THINGS
 SO MUCH EASIER FOR RITA...

245
00:14:35.567 --> 00:14:37.834
 BUT THAT WOULD BE WRONG.

246
00:14:41.834 --> 00:14:45.234
[ GROWLS ]

247
00:14:45.300 --> 00:14:46.667
 I LOVE HALLOWEEN --

248
00:14:46.734 --> 00:14:49.367
 THE ONE TIME OF YEAR
 WHEN EVERYONE WEARS A MASK...

249
00:14:49.434 --> 00:14:52.267
 NOT JUST ME.

250
00:14:52.334 --> 00:14:55.367
 PEOPLE THINK IT'S FUN
 TO PRETEND YOU'RE A MONSTER.

251
00:14:55.434 --> 00:14:58.601
 ME. I SPEND MY LIFE
 PRETENDING I'M NOT.

252
00:15:00.567 --> 00:15:02.234
 BROTHER. FRIEND. BOYFRIEND --

253
00:15:02.300 --> 00:15:04.534
 ALL PART
 OF MY COSTUME COLLECTION.

254
00:15:09.367 --> 00:15:11.701
 SOME PEOPLE MIGHT CALL ME
 A FRAUD.

255
00:15:11.767 --> 00:15:13.767
LET'S SEE IF IT WILL FIT.

256
00:15:15.267 --> 00:15:16.300
BOO!

257
00:15:16.367 --> 00:15:19.667
AAH!
YOU STABBED ME IN THE BACK!

258
00:15:19.734 --> 00:15:24.501
 I PREFER TO THINK OF MYSELF
 AS A MASTER OF DISGUISE.

259
00:15:24.567 --> 00:15:27.434
[ LAUGHS ]
THEY'RE SO EXCITED.

260
00:15:27.501 --> 00:15:30.801
SURE THEY ARE. THEY GET TO BINGE
ON SUGAR FOR AN ENTIRE DAY.

261
00:15:30.868 --> 00:15:32.167
WHO WOULDN'T LOVE THAT?

262
00:15:32.234 --> 00:15:35.067
WHAT ABOUT A COSTUME FOR YOU?
MAYBE THIS ONE?

263
00:15:35.133 --> 00:15:36.234
UM...

264
00:15:36.300 --> 00:15:39.133
NO. NO. I THINK
I'LL BE SNOW WHITE AGAIN.

265
00:15:39.200 --> 00:15:40.734
IT'S KIND OF TRADITION.

266
00:15:40.801 --> 00:15:43.000
OH.

267
00:15:43.067 --> 00:15:45.067
DEXTER. LOOK.
I'M A PRINCESS. TOO.

268
00:15:45.133 --> 00:15:47.767
JUST LIKE YOUR MOM --
TWO PERFECT PRINCESSES.

269
00:15:47.834 --> 00:15:50.234
LET ME GUESS.
YOU'RE GONNA BE A DWARF.

270
00:15:50.300 --> 00:15:54.400
NO WAY. I WANT TO BE JOE
FROM "BLUE'S CLUES."

271
00:15:54.467 --> 00:15:58.901
I KEEP TELLING HIM THAT
A RUGBY SHIRT IS NOT A COSTUME.

272
00:16:05.601 --> 00:16:08.934
 ANOTHER PHOTO
 FROM MY FAMILY ALBUM.

273
00:16:09.000 --> 00:16:13.033
 HE'S RE-CREATING MY PAST
 WITH TONY TUCCI'S BODY PARTS.

274
00:16:13.100 --> 00:16:15.467
 HE'S FORCING ME TO SEE THIS.

275
00:16:15.534 --> 00:16:18.367
NOBODY PAYING YOU TO STAND
AROUND AND GODDAMN STARE.

276
00:16:18.434 --> 00:16:21.634
I THOUGHT ANGEL WAS WORKING
THIS CASE. SERGEANT.

277
00:16:23.667 --> 00:16:24.934
SERGEANT?

278
00:16:28.200 --> 00:16:29.534
FRIENDS OF YOURS?

279
00:16:29.601 --> 00:16:32.567
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
WORRY ABOUT THIS.

280
00:16:32.634 --> 00:16:36.434
THE FOOT WAS SEVERED BETWEEN
THE TARSUS AND THE METATARSUS.

281
00:16:36.501 --> 00:16:40.567
THE WOUND IS CIRCULAR --
AGAIN. ALMOST SURGICAL.

282
00:16:40.634 --> 00:16:41.968
AND THERE'S BLOOD.

283
00:16:42.033 --> 00:16:44.133
GUY GIVES US BODY AFTER BODY
WITH NO BLOOD.

284
00:16:44.200 --> 00:16:45.701
WHY HE'S MAKING
A SWITCH NOW?

285
00:16:45.767 --> 00:16:47.400
HE'S TRYING
TO SEND A MESSAGE --

286
00:16:47.467 --> 00:16:50.501
ONE THAT'S MORE IMPORTANT
THAN HIS RITUAL NEED

287
00:16:50.567 --> 00:16:53.133
TO DRAIN THE BLOOD
AND WRAP THE PARTS.

288
00:16:53.200 --> 00:16:55.234
OKAY.
SO WHAT'S THE MESSAGE?

289
00:16:55.300 --> 00:16:56.868
I'M NOT SURE.

290
00:16:56.934 --> 00:16:59.801
WELL.
WHO'S HE SENDING IT TO?

291
00:16:59.868 --> 00:17:02.267
I CAN'T TELL YOU THAT.
EITHER.

292
00:17:03.634 --> 00:17:06.567
WHAT FUCKING GOOD
ARE YOU?

293
00:17:06.634 --> 00:17:09.534
NO FUCKING GOOD AT ALL.
APPARENTLY.

294
00:17:11.534 --> 00:17:14.400
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

295
00:17:14.467 --> 00:17:15.501
YOU OKAY?

296
00:17:15.567 --> 00:17:16.834
HE'S MOCKING ME.

297
00:17:16.901 --> 00:17:21.100
DON'T TAKE IT PERSONAL.
DOAKES HATES ALL YOU LAB GEEKS.

298
00:17:21.167 --> 00:17:23.968
WHO? OH.

299
00:17:24.033 --> 00:17:25.601
RELAX. BRO.
SORRY.

300
00:17:25.667 --> 00:17:28.634
I NEED TO BAG THIS PHOTO
UNDER THE BALL. DO YOU MIND?

301
00:17:47.067 --> 00:17:49.868
 HE KNOWS.

302
00:17:49.934 --> 00:17:53.834
 HE'S NOT CORRUPTING THE HAPPY
 HALLMARK IMAGES OF MY YOUTH.

303
00:17:53.901 --> 00:17:57.434
 HE'S REVEALING
 THE UGLY TRUTH BEHIND THEM.

304
00:17:57.501 --> 00:17:59.934
COME ON. SIMON.

305
00:18:00.000 --> 00:18:02.934
YOU WANT IT?
IT'S RIGHT THERE.

306
00:18:03.000 --> 00:18:04.834
OVER THERE.
OH. YEAH.

307
00:18:04.901 --> 00:18:05.901
GUYS. GIVE IT BACK!

308
00:18:05.968 --> 00:18:06.968
PASS IT OVER HERE.

309
00:18:07.033 --> 00:18:08.467
YOU GUYS.
GIVE IT BACK.

310
00:18:08.534 --> 00:18:10.501
COME ON. SIMON.
WHAT YOU GONNA DO?

311
00:18:10.567 --> 00:18:13.067
ALL RIGHT.
ENOUGH.

312
00:18:15.667 --> 00:18:17.634
GET OUT OF HERE.

313
00:18:21.467 --> 00:18:22.834
WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON?

314
00:18:22.901 --> 00:18:24.000
WE'RE JUST HAVING FUN.

315
00:18:24.067 --> 00:18:26.300
IT DIDN'T LOOK LIKE SIMON
WAS HAVING TOO MUCH FUN.

316
00:18:26.367 --> 00:18:28.100
YOU'RE ALWAYS TELLING ME
TO FIT IN.

317
00:18:28.167 --> 00:18:30.200
AND I'M JUST TRYING
TO BE PART OF THE TEAM.

318
00:18:30.267 --> 00:18:33.834
YOU CAN'T BE A BULLY.
DEXTER.

319
00:18:33.901 --> 00:18:35.734
FIRST OF ALL.
IT'S WRONG.

320
00:18:35.801 --> 00:18:38.267
SECONDLY.
PEOPLE REMEMBER BULLIES.

321
00:18:38.334 --> 00:18:40.567
PEOPLE LIKE ME --
COPS.

322
00:18:40.634 --> 00:18:43.968
A BULLY IS A FELONY
WAITING TO HAPPEN.

323
00:18:44.033 --> 00:18:45.767
SO...

324
00:18:45.834 --> 00:18:47.767
BLEND IN.

325
00:18:49.467 --> 00:18:51.033
GO ON.

326
00:19:00.934 --> 00:19:03.200
OFFICER MORGAN.
I HAVE AN ASSIGNMENT FOR YOU.

327
00:19:03.267 --> 00:19:05.200
I HEARD WE FOUND
A FOOT THIS MORNING.

328
00:19:05.267 --> 00:19:07.467
YOU WANT ME TO HEAD OUT
TO THE CRIME SCENE?

329
00:19:07.534 --> 00:19:08.868
NO.

330
00:19:08.934 --> 00:19:11.267
LOOK. WE PULLED THESE
FROM SECURITY CAMERAS

331
00:19:11.334 --> 00:19:13.601
AROUND THE BEACH --
STORES. HOTELS. ATMs.

332
00:19:13.667 --> 00:19:15.501
I WANT YOU TO CHECK
EVERY FRAME.

333
00:19:15.567 --> 00:19:17.000
OH.
YOU ARE SHITTING ME.

334
00:19:17.067 --> 00:19:18.234
IF WE'RE LUCKY.

335
00:19:18.300 --> 00:19:20.601
WE CAN SEE THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER
COMING AND GOING.

336
00:19:20.667 --> 00:19:22.400
WE HAVE TECHS
WHO CAN DO THIS.

337
00:19:22.467 --> 00:19:25.634
NOT ALL TECHS HAVE THE SKILL
TO SPOT SUSPICIOUS ACTIVITY.

338
00:19:25.701 --> 00:19:28.234
I'M TAKING A HUGE LEAP
OF FAITH THAT YOU DO.

339
00:19:28.300 --> 00:19:31.400
KEEP YOUR EYE OUT FOR ANOTHER
BOX OF SURVEILLANCE TAPES.

340
00:19:31.467 --> 00:19:34.767
IT'S ON ITS WAY
FROM THE NEW CRIME SCENE.

341
00:19:34.834 --> 00:19:37.834
[ SIGHS ]

342
00:19:56.968 --> 00:20:01.267
HEY. DOAKES. WHAT'S UP?
FUCK ANYONE'S WIFE LATELY?

343
00:20:06.234 --> 00:20:08.267
THANKS TO YOUR LITTLE
CHICKENSHIT STUNT.

344
00:20:08.334 --> 00:20:10.667
GUERRERO'S GUYS ARE TAILING ME
EVERYWHERE I GO.

345
00:20:10.734 --> 00:20:11.934
THAT'S NOT GOOD.
JAMES.

346
00:20:12.000 --> 00:20:13.467
YOU SHOULD
ALERT THE POLICE...

347
00:20:13.534 --> 00:20:15.167
UNLESS. OF COURSE.
FOR SOME REASON

348
00:20:15.234 --> 00:20:17.634
THE OFFICERS OF MIAMI METRO
WOULDN'T WANT TO HELP YOU --

349
00:20:17.701 --> 00:20:19.834
LIKE. YOU KNOW.
YOU FUCKED ONE OF THEIR WIVES.

350
00:20:19.901 --> 00:20:22.300
YOU THINK THIS IS A JOKE.

351
00:20:22.367 --> 00:20:24.667
I'M GONNA END UP DEAD.
IT'S JUST A MATTER OF WHEN.

352
00:20:24.734 --> 00:20:26.601
YOU SHOULD HAVE
THOUGHT OF THAT

353
00:20:26.667 --> 00:20:28.901
BEFORE YOU STUCK YOUR DICK
IN MY SISTER.

354
00:20:28.968 --> 00:20:30.968
YOU'RE RIGHT.

355
00:20:31.033 --> 00:20:33.834
I SHOULD HAVE WAITED
UNTIL THE DIVORCE CAME THROUGH.

356
00:20:35.834 --> 00:20:37.501
BULLSHIT.

357
00:20:37.567 --> 00:20:38.801
[ SCOFFS ]

358
00:20:38.868 --> 00:20:40.067
WHAT?
SHE DIDN'T TELL YOU?

359
00:20:40.133 --> 00:20:41.901
SHE FILED THE PAPERS.
JACKASS.

360
00:20:41.968 --> 00:20:44.234
YOU DON'T BELIEVE ME.
ASK THE CAPTAIN.

361
00:20:44.300 --> 00:20:46.767
HE TRIED TO PULL RICKY
OUT OF HIS ASSIGNMENT.

362
00:20:46.834 --> 00:20:48.767
BUT RICKY DIDN'T WANT
TO COME OUT.

363
00:20:48.834 --> 00:20:51.367
OF COURSE NOT. HIS JOB WAS
TO BRING DOWN GUERRERO.

364
00:20:51.434 --> 00:20:53.601
IT WAS HIS JOB
TO PROTECT HIS WIFE.

365
00:20:55.067 --> 00:20:58.367
RICKY'S THE MOTHERFUCKER
WHO GOT HER KILLED.

366
00:20:58.434 --> 00:21:01.167
YOU BACKED THE WRONG COP.
ASSHOLE.

367
00:21:05.834 --> 00:21:10.834
LET'S GO. GUYS.
TIME FOR SCHOOL.

368
00:21:10.901 --> 00:21:13.200
GUYS? COME ON.

369
00:21:13.267 --> 00:21:15.501
YOU DON'T WANT TO BE
IN THE HALLOWEEN PARADE?

370
00:21:15.567 --> 00:21:17.701
[ DOG BARKING ]

371
00:21:17.767 --> 00:21:19.601
[ SIGHS ]

372
00:21:19.667 --> 00:21:21.934
[ BARKING CONTINUES ]

373
00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:25.033
SHUT UP!

374
00:21:25.100 --> 00:21:26.934
SHUT UP! JUST --

375
00:21:27.000 --> 00:21:29.300
[ SIGHS ]

376
00:21:29.367 --> 00:21:31.234
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT YOUR DOG.

377
00:21:31.300 --> 00:21:32.634
I TALKED
TO YOUR BOYFRIEND.

378
00:21:32.701 --> 00:21:34.734
MY KIDS ARE EXHAUSTED.

379
00:21:34.801 --> 00:21:36.968
ALL RIGHT.
WHEN IT COMES TO MY KIDS.

380
00:21:37.033 --> 00:21:38.100
I STOP BEING NICE.

381
00:21:38.167 --> 00:21:40.501
SO I NEED YOU TO BRING HIM
IN AT NIGHT.

382
00:21:40.567 --> 00:21:41.868
FEED HIM ON A SCHEDULE.

383
00:21:41.934 --> 00:21:44.567
AND TAKE HIM FOR SOME EXERCISE
EVERY NOW AND --

384
00:21:44.634 --> 00:21:47.033
[ CHUCKLES ]

385
00:21:47.100 --> 00:21:49.467
I'M SORRY.
IS THIS FUNNY?

386
00:21:49.534 --> 00:21:52.334
NO. NO. NO.
IT'S -- IT'S SAD.

387
00:21:52.400 --> 00:21:56.067
BUT YOU'RE FUNNY.
LOOK AT YOU. ALL TOUGH.

388
00:21:56.133 --> 00:21:57.934
[ CHUCKLES ]

389
00:21:58.033 --> 00:22:00.968
I-I'M GONNA CALL THE POLICE.
I CAN DO THAT.

390
00:22:01.033 --> 00:22:02.434
THERE'S NOTHING
YOU CAN DO.

391
00:22:02.501 --> 00:22:04.400
THE COPS WILL TELL ME
TO KEEP HIM QUIET.

392
00:22:04.467 --> 00:22:06.400
AND I'LL SAY I WILL.
AND THEN THEY'LL LEAVE.

393
00:22:06.467 --> 00:22:09.167
AND HE'LL GO BACK
TO DOING WHAT HE DOES.

394
00:22:09.234 --> 00:22:12.033
BUT YOU'RE FUNNY.

395
00:22:12.100 --> 00:22:13.667
[ CHUCKLES ]

396
00:22:14.767 --> 00:22:18.634
[ DOG BARKING ]

397
00:22:18.701 --> 00:22:21.534
[ CHUCKLES EVILLY ]

398
00:22:25.100 --> 00:22:27.367
[ BARKING CONTINUES ]

399
00:22:41.400 --> 00:22:43.234
 UNLIKE HARRY.

400
00:22:43.300 --> 00:22:46.234
 MY NEW FRIEND DOESN'T PLACE
 MUCH VALUE IN BLENDING IN.

401
00:22:46.300 --> 00:22:48.901
 HE WANTS ME TO SEE WHO HE IS
 AND WHAT HE DOES.

402
00:22:50.567 --> 00:22:54.701
 EVERYTHING ABOUT HIM IS BRAZEN.
 AUTHENTIC.

403
00:22:56.501 --> 00:22:57.567
 WHAT DOES THAT MAKE ME?

404
00:22:57.634 --> 00:22:58.934
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

405
00:22:59.000 --> 00:23:00.834
CRAP.

406
00:23:03.701 --> 00:23:06.000
[ SIGHS ]

407
00:23:08.234 --> 00:23:09.667
YOU OKAY. MAN?
NO.

408
00:23:09.734 --> 00:23:11.801
HEY. DON'T LET THIS BASTARD
GET TO YOU.

409
00:23:11.868 --> 00:23:14.033
YOU'RE THE BEST BLOOD EXPERT
IN THE STATE.

410
00:23:14.100 --> 00:23:16.400
AND WE NEED YOU
TO STAY WITH THIS. MY FRIEND.

411
00:23:16.467 --> 00:23:18.100
I'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

412
00:23:18.167 --> 00:23:19.234
WAIT.

413
00:23:19.300 --> 00:23:23.601
BEFORE YOU GET BACK TO WORK.
CHECK THIS OUT.

414
00:23:23.667 --> 00:23:25.200
HUH?

415
00:23:26.767 --> 00:23:28.267
WHAT IS THAT.
A BUTTERFLY?

416
00:23:28.334 --> 00:23:29.901
NO. SOCIO.

417
00:23:29.968 --> 00:23:33.267
IT'S A DIAMOND-STUDDED
FOUR-LEAF CLOVER.

418
00:23:33.334 --> 00:23:35.934
I'M. UH.
I'M GIVING IT TO NINA

419
00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:38.400
FOR OUR ANNIVERSARY
TOMORROW NIGHT.

420
00:23:38.467 --> 00:23:41.167
OH. CONGRATULATIONS.
HOW MANY YEARS?

421
00:23:41.234 --> 00:23:43.567
10 YEARS SHE'S BEEN
MY LUCKY CHARM NOW.

422
00:23:43.634 --> 00:23:45.667
TIN IS
THE TRADITIONAL GIFT.

423
00:23:45.734 --> 00:23:48.167
BUT I DIDN'T THINK
SHE'D WANT A TIN CLOVER.

424
00:23:48.234 --> 00:23:51.167
NO.
IT'S PROBABLY A GOOD PLAN.

425
00:23:51.234 --> 00:23:53.501
ARE YOU SURE
THAT'S NOT A BUTTERFLY?

426
00:23:55.601 --> 00:23:58.767
WELL. IT DOES KIND OF LOOK
LIKE A BUG.

427
00:24:00.801 --> 00:24:03.634
THIS CAN'T BE RIGHT.

428
00:24:03.701 --> 00:24:05.367
WHAT'S UP?

429
00:24:05.434 --> 00:24:07.133
YOU SEE THAT?
YOU SEE IT?

430
00:24:07.200 --> 00:24:09.067
I DON'T KNOW.
WHAT DO I SEE?

431
00:24:09.133 --> 00:24:10.868
THE BLOOD FLOW
IN THE HAND

432
00:24:10.934 --> 00:24:13.767
SUGGESTED THE HEART WAS STILL
PUMPING WHEN IT WAS SEVERED.

433
00:24:13.834 --> 00:24:15.667
MEAN SON OF A BITCH.
NO DOUBT.

434
00:24:15.734 --> 00:24:16.868
BUT LOOK AT THE FOOT.

435
00:24:16.934 --> 00:24:19.567
IT'S THE SAME BLOOD FLOW.
PLUS THE LIVIDITY.

436
00:24:19.634 --> 00:24:22.434
LOOK. IT'S THE SAME BRUISING.
SAME ASHEN COLOR.

437
00:24:22.501 --> 00:24:25.934
SAME LEVEL OF DECOMPOSITION
AS THE HAND THE DAY WE FOUND IT.

438
00:24:26.000 --> 00:24:29.467
BUT...
WE FOUND THEM A DAY APART.

439
00:24:29.534 --> 00:24:31.667
I KNOW.

440
00:24:33.834 --> 00:24:35.434
 LOS SANTOS.

441
00:24:35.501 --> 00:24:37.634
HERE'S A PICTURE.
HOLLYWOOD. FL--

442
00:24:37.701 --> 00:24:40.467
L.T..
YOU GOT TO LISTEN TO HIM.

443
00:24:40.534 --> 00:24:44.200
IT'S THE GUARD. TUCCI --
I THINK HE'S ALIVE.

444
00:24:44.267 --> 00:24:46.400
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

445
00:24:46.467 --> 00:24:49.234
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER IS
KEEPING HIM ALIVE

446
00:24:49.300 --> 00:24:50.834
TO PERFORM AMPUTATIONS.

447
00:24:50.901 --> 00:24:52.400
TUCCI'S ALIVE?

448
00:24:52.467 --> 00:24:55.000
BOTH LIMBS WERE TAKEN
FROM A LIVE BODY.

449
00:24:55.067 --> 00:24:57.300
AND WE FOUND THEM
24 HOURS APART.

450
00:24:57.367 --> 00:24:59.400
THAT'S NOT ALL.
TELL THEM. DEXTER.

451
00:24:59.467 --> 00:25:01.534
IF THE HAND CAME OFF YESTERDAY
AT 7:00 A.M.

452
00:25:01.601 --> 00:25:03.400
AND THE FOOT THIS MORNING
AT 7:00...

453
00:25:03.467 --> 00:25:05.467
WE GET ANOTHER BODY PART
FIRST THING TOMORROW.

454
00:25:05.534 --> 00:25:06.801
BUT HE'S ALIVE.

455
00:25:06.868 --> 00:25:08.834
PUT TOGETHER A TASK FORCE.

456
00:25:08.901 --> 00:25:10.734
I WANT ALL AVAILABLE PERSONNEL
ON THIS.

457
00:25:10.801 --> 00:25:14.434
AND PUT A PRIORITY STATUS ON ALL
FORENSICS RELATED TO THIS CASE.

458
00:25:14.501 --> 00:25:16.501
CAPTAIN MATTHEWS. PLEASE.

459
00:25:16.567 --> 00:25:19.601
HAVE HIM CALL ME BACK
IMMEDIATELY.

460
00:25:44.167 --> 00:25:46.634
MRS. TUCCI?

461
00:25:46.701 --> 00:25:49.200
MARIA LaGUERTA.

462
00:25:49.267 --> 00:25:52.534
I HAVE SOME AMAZING NEWS
FOR YOU.

463
00:25:52.601 --> 00:25:56.901
WE BELIEVE YOUR SON IS ALIVE.

464
00:25:56.968 --> 00:26:00.667
NO. NO. WE HAVEN'T.
BUT I PROMISE WE WILL.

465
00:26:03.501 --> 00:26:05.234
NO. THANK YOU.

466
00:26:05.300 --> 00:26:07.734
YES. YES.

467
00:26:07.801 --> 00:26:10.501
OKAY. WE'LL BE IN TOUCH.
BYE.

468
00:26:16.634 --> 00:26:18.767
Doakes: WE'VE GOT
A LIVE BODY NOW. PEOPLE.

469
00:26:18.834 --> 00:26:21.167
WE WANT TO FIND TUCCI
WHILE HE'S STILL BREATHING.

470
00:26:21.234 --> 00:26:23.868
THAT MEANS TRYING TO FIGURE OUT
WHERE TOMORROW'S DROP IS

471
00:26:23.934 --> 00:26:25.400
SO WE CATCH OUR MAN IN THE ACT.

472
00:26:25.467 --> 00:26:26.501
ANY IDEAS?

473
00:26:28.734 --> 00:26:30.834
DON'T FORGET THE PHOTOS.
THEY'RE NEW.

474
00:26:30.901 --> 00:26:34.167
THANK YOU. OFFICER MORGAN.
WE'RE DOING JUST FINE OUT HERE.

475
00:26:34.234 --> 00:26:37.100
WHY DO WE THINK
HE'S TAKING PHOTOS?

476
00:26:37.167 --> 00:26:38.701
HE WANTS TO BE REMEMBERED.

477
00:26:38.767 --> 00:26:40.901
YOU USE PHOTOS
TO RECORD MEMORIES.

478
00:26:40.968 --> 00:26:44.734
 I ALMOST FEEL SORRY FOR THEM.
 TRYING TO PUT TOGETHER A PUZZLE

479
00:26:44.801 --> 00:26:47.968
 WHEN THEY DON'T KNOW PIECES
 ARE MISSING FROM THE BOX --

480
00:26:48.033 --> 00:26:50.234
 PIECES HE GAVE ME.

481
00:26:54.167 --> 00:26:59.501
 HE WANTS ME TO PLAY THE GAME
 HIS WAY.

482
00:26:59.567 --> 00:27:01.567
OKAY.
WHAT ELSE COULD IT BE?

483
00:27:01.634 --> 00:27:03.200
CHANGE.

484
00:27:05.868 --> 00:27:07.868
YOU GOT SOMETHING TO SAY.
SPEAK UP.

485
00:27:07.934 --> 00:27:09.367
THE BEACH CHANGED NAMES.

486
00:27:09.434 --> 00:27:12.200
THE OFFICE PARK USED TO BE
A SOCCER FIELD.

487
00:27:12.267 --> 00:27:13.567
HE'S DUMPING
THE BODY PARTS

488
00:27:13.634 --> 00:27:15.434
IN PLACES THAT USED TO BE
SOMETHING ELSE.

489
00:27:15.501 --> 00:27:17.634
OKAY.

490
00:27:17.701 --> 00:27:18.968
PLACES THAT HAVE CHANGED.

491
00:27:19.033 --> 00:27:20.334
LET'S MAKE A LIST.

492
00:27:20.400 --> 00:27:22.701
ASSIGN SURVEILLANCE TO EACH
LOCATION FOR THE MORNING.

493
00:27:22.767 --> 00:27:25.067
SOUTH BEACH USED TO BE
A MANGROVE SWAMP.

494
00:27:25.133 --> 00:27:28.133
HOMESTEAD PARK WAS ORIGINALLY
AN AIR FORCE BASE. RIGHT?

495
00:27:28.200 --> 00:27:31.767
THEY TURNED VERSACE'S MANSION
INTO A HOTEL.

496
00:27:31.834 --> 00:27:33.868
THANK YOU.
OFFICER MORGAN.

497
00:27:33.934 --> 00:27:37.334
THE WHOLE CITY OF MIAMI
REINVENTS ITSELF EVERY 5 YEARS.

498
00:27:37.400 --> 00:27:40.133
THEN WE'LL STAY UP ALL NIGHT
UNTIL OUR LIST IS COMPLETE.

499
00:27:40.200 --> 00:27:44.934
* I ONCE WAS LOST *

500
00:27:45.000 --> 00:27:49.400
* BUT NOW I'M FOUND *

501
00:27:49.467 --> 00:27:52.534
* WAS BLIND *

502
00:27:52.601 --> 00:27:58.501
* BUT NOW I SEE *

503
00:28:05.534 --> 00:28:09.200
LIEUTENANT.

504
00:28:14.901 --> 00:28:16.400
ANYTHING?

505
00:28:18.300 --> 00:28:23.267
WELL. I AM SO GLAD
YOU COULD MAKE IT.

506
00:28:24.434 --> 00:28:27.167
WELL. I JUST CAME BY
TO SHOW MY SUPPORT.

507
00:28:28.701 --> 00:28:31.567
IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME
SINCE I'VE BEEN TO CHURCH.

508
00:28:33.667 --> 00:28:35.934
EXCUSE ME. EVERYONE.
EXCUSE ME.

509
00:28:36.000 --> 00:28:38.400
UM. I WOULD LIKE
TO INTRODUCE YOU

510
00:28:38.467 --> 00:28:40.133
TO SOMEONE VERY SPECIAL.

511
00:28:40.200 --> 00:28:42.601
THIS IS MARIA LaGUERTA.

512
00:28:42.667 --> 00:28:48.000
SHE'S THE POLICEWOMAN
LOOKING FOR TONY.

513
00:28:48.067 --> 00:28:49.434
NOT JUST ME.

514
00:28:49.501 --> 00:28:52.701
ACTUALLY.
THERE'S A LOT OF US LOOKING.

515
00:28:52.767 --> 00:28:57.400
YOU BROUGHT US ALL HERE TOGETHER
BY GIVING US HOPE.

516
00:29:01.634 --> 00:29:06.901
MAY THE LORD BLESS YOU
AND GUIDE YOU. MARIA.

517
00:29:06.968 --> 00:29:12.367
THIS IS SAINT ANTHONY.
PATRON SAINT OF --

518
00:29:12.434 --> 00:29:14.300
THE LOST.

519
00:29:17.133 --> 00:29:19.000
FIND HIM.

520
00:29:21.501 --> 00:29:23.167
OKAY.

521
00:29:23.234 --> 00:29:26.267
I TRIED TO APOLOGIZE. BUT I
COULDN'T GET A WORD IN EDGEWISE.

522
00:29:26.334 --> 00:29:27.934
AND YOU WANTED
TO APOLOGIZE WHY?

523
00:29:28.000 --> 00:29:30.400
YOU DON'T THINK I SHOULD.
THE WAY I WENT AFTER HER SON?

524
00:29:30.467 --> 00:29:32.501
YEAH.
YOU DID FUCK THAT UP.

525
00:29:32.567 --> 00:29:34.667
[ SIGHS ]
YEAH.

526
00:29:34.734 --> 00:29:37.767
I CRUCIFIED HIM
WITHOUT HAVING ALL THE FACTS.

527
00:29:37.834 --> 00:29:41.300
[ SIGHS ] I NEED TO TELL HER
THAT I'M SORRY.

528
00:29:41.367 --> 00:29:44.400
I NEED TO LET HER KNOW
THAT I'M SORRY.

529
00:29:44.467 --> 00:29:46.033
I NEED TO TELL HER.

530
00:29:46.100 --> 00:29:49.133
WHO IS THAT GONNA MAKE
FEEL BETTER. YOU OR HER?

531
00:29:49.200 --> 00:29:52.801
LEAVE THAT WOMAN ALONE
WITH HER CANDLES AND "KUMBAYA."

532
00:29:58.701 --> 00:30:00.133
SO. WHERE WE AT?

533
00:30:00.200 --> 00:30:03.434
I ADDED ADDITIONAL PATROLS
AT DOLPHIN STADIUM.

534
00:30:03.501 --> 00:30:06.367
BAYSIDE MARKETPLACE.
AND CASA CASUARINA.

535
00:30:06.434 --> 00:30:09.200
THAT'S EVERYBODY WE HAVE OUT
IN THE FIELD --

536
00:30:09.267 --> 00:30:11.267
HOMICIDE. ROBBERY.
OFF-DUTY PATROL.

537
00:30:11.334 --> 00:30:12.434
SO WHAT'S NEXT?

538
00:30:12.501 --> 00:30:14.667
WHAT'S NEXT
IS YOU SHOULD GO HOME.

539
00:30:14.734 --> 00:30:17.667
YOU'VE HAD THE SHIT KICKED OUT
OF YOU ALL DAY.

540
00:30:17.734 --> 00:30:18.934
I LIKE IT HERE WITH YOU.

541
00:30:19.033 --> 00:30:21.200
YOU'RE THE ONLY PERSON
PEOPLE HATE MORE THAN ME.

542
00:30:21.267 --> 00:30:22.634
[ Laughing ]
FUCK YOU.

543
00:30:22.701 --> 00:30:24.067
[ CHUCKLING ]

544
00:30:24.133 --> 00:30:26.067
COME ON.
LET'S BOTH GET OUT OF HERE.

545
00:30:26.133 --> 00:30:28.133
NOTHING LEFT
BUT THE WAITING NOW. ANYWAY.

546
00:30:38.167 --> 00:30:40.033
HEY!

547
00:30:40.100 --> 00:30:43.167
OFFICER MORGAN.

548
00:30:43.234 --> 00:30:47.334
CALL ME ON MY CELLPHONE
IF YOU FIND ANYTHING.

549
00:31:02.634 --> 00:31:04.300
Doakes:
SON OF A BITCH.

550
00:31:07.534 --> 00:31:08.801
FUCK THIS.

551
00:31:15.133 --> 00:31:16.968
WHAT? HUH?
WANT A PIECE OF ME?

552
00:31:17.033 --> 00:31:19.167
HUH? HUH? HUH?

553
00:31:19.234 --> 00:31:21.367
FUCKING ASSHOLE!

554
00:31:24.000 --> 00:31:26.868
DEBRA: I will pay you
$1 million

555
00:31:26.934 --> 00:31:28.968
if you help me figure out

556
00:31:29.033 --> 00:31:31.801
where the next piece of Tucci's
gonna show up.

557
00:31:31.868 --> 00:31:33.801
I'M AFRAID
I'M LOST ON THIS ONE. DEB.

558
00:31:33.868 --> 00:31:36.434
IT'S LIKE IT'S STARING ME
RIGHT IN THE FACE. BUT --

559
00:31:36.501 --> 00:31:37.901
$1 million.

560
00:31:37.968 --> 00:31:40.100
YOU DON'T HAVE $1 MILLION.

561
00:31:40.167 --> 00:31:42.033
I'LL STEAL IT
FROM EVIDENCE.

562
00:31:42.100 --> 00:31:44.868
I'VE BEEN STUCK
IN A GODDAMN FISHBOWL ALL DAY.

563
00:31:44.934 --> 00:31:48.000
I WANT TO BE PART OF THE HUNT.
I'M ALMOST OFF DUTY.

564
00:31:48.067 --> 00:31:49.501
Sorry. sister.

565
00:31:49.567 --> 00:31:51.467
$2 MILLION.

566
00:31:51.534 --> 00:31:54.300
I KNOW YOU MADE
A LIST OF LOCATIONS.

567
00:31:54.367 --> 00:31:57.701
Just pick your favorite spot.
We'll stake it out together.

568
00:31:57.767 --> 00:32:01.067
 MY FAVORITE SPOT.
 OF COURSE.

569
00:32:01.133 --> 00:32:02.334
Come on.

570
00:32:02.400 --> 00:32:03.667
I WANT TO PLAY.

571
00:32:07.634 --> 00:32:08.734
DEB. I GOT TO GO.

572
00:32:08.801 --> 00:32:10.801
WE'LL COMPARE NOTES TOMORROW.
OKAY?

573
00:32:17.067 --> 00:32:19.634
 I USED TO LOVE THIS PLACE --

574
00:32:19.701 --> 00:32:22.801
 THE BULLDOZERS PRESSING
 GARBAGE. LAYER AFTER LAYER.

575
00:32:22.868 --> 00:32:25.400
 RIGHT INTO THE EARTH ITSELF.
 BURYING IT.

576
00:32:25.467 --> 00:32:26.634
 HIDING IT.

577
00:32:26.701 --> 00:32:29.734
 I FOUND IT SOOTHING.

578
00:32:32.167 --> 00:32:35.901
 BUT IT WASN'T CONDOS BACK THEN.

579
00:32:38.300 --> 00:32:41.467
 THIS HAS TO BE THE RIGHT PLACE.

580
00:32:44.667 --> 00:32:48.167
 SO WHAT AM I MISSING?

581
00:33:14.901 --> 00:33:15.901
[ GASPS ]

582
00:33:18.601 --> 00:33:22.234
SORRY ABOUT THAT.
GO BACK TO SLEEP.

583
00:33:22.300 --> 00:33:24.334
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

584
00:33:26.467 --> 00:33:30.000
HELLO.

585
00:33:30.067 --> 00:33:31.634
WOMAN: Mr. Morgan?
Dispatch.

586
00:33:31.701 --> 00:33:34.200
You've been called
to the McCaffrey pumpkin patch.

587
00:33:34.267 --> 00:33:36.267
Do you need the address?

588
00:33:36.334 --> 00:33:39.434
NO.
I KNOW EXACTLY WHERE IT IS.

589
00:33:41.901 --> 00:33:43.968
ARE YOU OKAY?

590
00:33:44.033 --> 00:33:46.534
ARE YOU KIDDING?
THAT WAS AWESOME.

591
00:33:46.601 --> 00:33:49.033
YOU'VE GOT SOME HAY
IN YOUR HAIR.

592
00:33:49.100 --> 00:33:50.067
WHERE?

593
00:33:50.133 --> 00:33:51.200
RIGHT THERE!

594
00:33:51.267 --> 00:33:53.033
OKAY. OKAY. OKAY. OKAY.

595
00:33:53.100 --> 00:33:55.801
ENOUGH. ENOUGH. YOU TWO.
COME ON.

596
00:33:55.868 --> 00:33:58.734
LET ME TAKE A PICTURE OF YOU
AND THE KIDS.

597
00:33:58.801 --> 00:34:01.467
YOU'LL MISS THESE MOMENTS
WHEN THEY'RE OLDER.

598
00:34:01.534 --> 00:34:03.133
THANKS.

599
00:34:03.200 --> 00:34:05.467
IT'S GREAT TO SEE YOU HAVING
SUCH A GOOD TIME. DEX.

600
00:34:05.534 --> 00:34:06.634
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

601
00:34:06.701 --> 00:34:08.767
THIS HAY'S GIVING ME
A TOTAL ALLERGY ATTACK.

602
00:34:08.834 --> 00:34:11.200
AND WE'RE GOING AROUND
IN CIRCLES ON A PUMPKIN PATCH.

603
00:34:11.267 --> 00:34:12.767
READY?

604
00:34:12.834 --> 00:34:14.033
SMILE!

605
00:34:18.234 --> 00:34:19.701
WHAT DO WE HAVE?

606
00:34:19.767 --> 00:34:23.100
ANKLE TO KNEE.
HE'S MOVING UP THE LEG.

607
00:34:23.167 --> 00:34:25.901
[ SIGHS ]

608
00:34:25.968 --> 00:34:29.467
YOU THINK TUCCI'S
STILL ALIVE?

609
00:34:29.534 --> 00:34:31.067
IF HE IS.
HE WON'T BE FOR LONG.

610
00:34:36.667 --> 00:34:38.934
UNLESS YOU'RE TOTING
A PORTABLE DVD PLAYER.

611
00:34:39.000 --> 00:34:41.734
YOU BETTER BE FINISHED WATCHING
THAT SECURITY FOOTAGE.

612
00:34:41.801 --> 00:34:44.300
I AM ON A BREAK.
I'M ON MY OWN TIME.

613
00:34:44.367 --> 00:34:47.534
SO YOU ARE. BUT YOUR SHIFT
STARTS IN TWO HOURS.

614
00:34:47.601 --> 00:34:50.734
SO IF I WERE YOU.
I'D HEAD BACK TO THE STATION.

615
00:34:50.801 --> 00:34:53.934
TRAFFIC AT THIS HOUR'S
A BITCH.

616
00:34:54.000 --> 00:34:57.534
SPEAKING OF BITCH...

617
00:34:57.601 --> 00:35:00.501
DIDN'T DAD BRING US HERE ONCE
WHEN WE WERE KIDS?

618
00:35:00.567 --> 00:35:01.634
I DON'T REMEMBER.

619
00:35:01.701 --> 00:35:04.400
HEY. DEXTER. COME HERE.
TAKE A LOOK AT THIS.

620
00:35:04.467 --> 00:35:05.968
EXCUSE US.

621
00:35:06.033 --> 00:35:08.300
SHE'S RIGHT. YOU KNOW.
ABOUT THE TRAFFIC.

622
00:35:11.868 --> 00:35:13.901
IT'S INTERESTING.

623
00:35:13.968 --> 00:35:16.501
THERE'S NO SIGN OF INFECTION
WHERE THE FOOT WAS CUT OFF.

624
00:35:16.567 --> 00:35:18.901
LIKE HE GAVE TUCCI
PROPHYLACTIC ANTIBIOTICS

625
00:35:18.968 --> 00:35:20.634
BEFORE AMPUTATING.

626
00:35:20.701 --> 00:35:24.234
AT LEAST HE'S LOOKING
AFTER HIS PATIENT.

627
00:35:24.300 --> 00:35:28.701
HEY. CHECK THIS OUT.

628
00:35:28.767 --> 00:35:32.033
IS THIS APPROPRIATE?

629
00:35:32.100 --> 00:35:36.367
IT'S OUR ANNIVERSARY...
AND IT'S THE BIG ONE.

630
00:35:36.434 --> 00:35:38.501
NINA DESERVES THE BEST.

631
00:35:40.501 --> 00:35:42.534
"OX"?

632
00:35:42.601 --> 00:35:45.734
NO. FUCK!

633
00:35:45.801 --> 00:35:48.834
WHAT'S THE MATTER WITH YOU?
IT'S X's AND O's.

634
00:35:48.901 --> 00:35:50.501
LIKE TIC-TAC-TOE?

635
00:35:50.567 --> 00:35:53.400
NO.
LIKE HUGS AND KISSES.

636
00:35:53.467 --> 00:35:56.934
DIAMOND-FILLED HUGS AND KISSES
IN A WHITE-GOLD SETTING.

637
00:35:57.000 --> 00:36:00.701
WELL. THAT'S GOOD. 'CAUSE YOU
WOULDN'T WANT IT TO LOOK LIKE

638
00:36:00.767 --> 00:36:03.267
SOMEONE'S PLAYING TIC-TAC-TOE
ON HER HEAD.

639
00:36:07.567 --> 00:36:09.567
GOD DAMN IT.

640
00:36:14.100 --> 00:36:16.400
WHERE'S MOM?

641
00:36:16.467 --> 00:36:18.067
SHE HAD TO RUN A FEW ERRANDS

642
00:36:18.133 --> 00:36:20.734
BEFORE SHE TAKES YOU TWO
TRICK-OR-TREATING.

643
00:36:20.801 --> 00:36:23.334
BUT I'M TOO TIRED
TO GO TRICK-OR-TREATING.

644
00:36:23.400 --> 00:36:25.400
I HEARD YOU TWO WERE UP
A LOT LAST NIGHT.

645
00:36:25.467 --> 00:36:27.000
IT WAS THAT DAMN DOG.

646
00:36:27.067 --> 00:36:29.601
HEY. CODE. GROWN-UP LANGUAGE
IS FOR GROWN-UPS.

647
00:36:29.667 --> 00:36:32.501
I DON'T THINK THAT DOG WILL BE
BOTHERING YOU ANYMORE.

648
00:36:32.567 --> 00:36:34.167
HOW DO YOU KNOW?

649
00:36:34.234 --> 00:36:36.033
MY MYSTIC POWERS
TOLD ME.

650
00:36:36.100 --> 00:36:38.300
I HEARD LINDSAY LOHAN
SAY "DAMN."

651
00:36:38.367 --> 00:36:41.467
ALL RIGHT. TELL YOU WHAT --
I'LL MAKE YOU A DEAL.

652
00:36:41.534 --> 00:36:44.567
WHEN YOU BECOME A ROCK STAR.
YOU CAN SWEAR. TOO.

653
00:36:44.634 --> 00:36:46.701
Woman:
WALTER! WALTER!

654
00:36:46.767 --> 00:36:49.000
YOU'RE RIGHT.
HE'S GONE.

655
00:36:49.067 --> 00:36:50.067
Shh!

656
00:36:51.234 --> 00:36:53.234
WHERE'S MY DOG?!
WHAT DID YOU DO WITH IT?!

657
00:36:55.300 --> 00:36:56.934
[ BARKING ]

658
00:37:06.667 --> 00:37:08.133
[ BARKING CONTINUES ]

659
00:37:11.534 --> 00:37:13.868
ALL RIGHT.
HERE HE IS.

660
00:37:13.934 --> 00:37:18.467
JUST REMEMBER TO WALK HIM.
FEED HIM. AND LOVE HIM.

661
00:37:18.534 --> 00:37:20.801
OKAY?

662
00:37:20.868 --> 00:37:24.701
MY NIECES ARE SHY SOMETIMES.
GIRLS. SAY THANK YOU TO RITA.

663
00:37:24.767 --> 00:37:26.434
THANK YOU.THANK YOU.

664
00:37:26.501 --> 00:37:27.667
[ CHUCKLES ]

665
00:37:27.734 --> 00:37:30.601
THEY ALREADY MADE A DOGGY BED --
SWEATERS. TOWELS.

666
00:37:30.667 --> 00:37:33.868
IT ACTUALLY LOOKS MORE
COMFORTABLE THAN MY BED.

667
00:37:33.934 --> 00:37:36.400
I KNEW THIS WOULD BE
A PERFECT FIT.

668
00:37:36.467 --> 00:37:39.501
YOU DID A GOOD THING. RITA.
THANK YOU.

669
00:37:43.868 --> 00:37:47.000
 HARRY WAS THE ONLY ONE
 WHO SAW ME --

670
00:37:47.067 --> 00:37:49.100
 REALLY SAW ME --

671
00:37:49.167 --> 00:37:50.834
 SO HE TAUGHT ME TO HIDE.

672
00:37:50.901 --> 00:37:53.968
 THAT'S WHAT'S KEPT ME SAFE.

673
00:37:54.033 --> 00:37:58.400
 BUT SOMETIMES. I'M NOT SURE
 WHERE HARRY'S VISION OF ME ENDS

674
00:37:58.467 --> 00:38:01.200
 AND THE REAL ME STARTS.

675
00:38:01.267 --> 00:38:04.133
 IF I'M JUST A COLLECTION
 OF LEARNED BEHAVIORS --

676
00:38:04.200 --> 00:38:07.200
 BITS AND PIECES OF HARRY --
 MAYBE MY NEW FRIEND IS RIGHT.

677
00:38:07.267 --> 00:38:09.067
 MAYBE I AM A FRAUD.

678
00:38:09.133 --> 00:38:11.067
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

679
00:38:24.467 --> 00:38:26.033
HI.

680
00:38:26.100 --> 00:38:27.901
HEY.

681
00:38:29.467 --> 00:38:32.000
[ CHUCKLES ]

682
00:38:32.067 --> 00:38:33.567
WHERE'S ASTOR AND CODY?

683
00:38:33.634 --> 00:38:38.234
THEY'RE PASSED OUT
IN A SUGAR COMA AT COLLEEN'S.

684
00:38:39.934 --> 00:38:43.334
UM. CAN I COME IN?

685
00:38:43.400 --> 00:38:45.968
OH. YEAH. SURE.
SORRY.

686
00:38:53.267 --> 00:38:54.501
I SHOULD WARN YOU.

687
00:38:54.567 --> 00:38:57.067
I HAVEN'T REALLY BEEN MYSELF
LATELY.

688
00:38:57.133 --> 00:39:00.267
WELL.
MAYBE I CAN CHEER YOU UP.

689
00:39:05.434 --> 00:39:06.801
WHOA.

690
00:39:06.868 --> 00:39:09.100
[ Laughing ]
TRICK OR TREAT.

691
00:39:12.701 --> 00:39:14.434
AH.

692
00:39:14.501 --> 00:39:16.467
YOU LOOK GREAT.

693
00:39:20.634 --> 00:39:22.601
WHO ARE YOU?

694
00:39:22.667 --> 00:39:25.300
LARA CROFT.

695
00:39:25.367 --> 00:39:26.701
"TOMB RAIDER."

696
00:39:26.767 --> 00:39:29.033
OH.

697
00:39:29.100 --> 00:39:32.033
YOU RAID TOMBS DRESSED
LIKE THAT?

698
00:39:32.100 --> 00:39:33.968
THAT'S IMPRESSIVE.

699
00:39:34.033 --> 00:39:36.200
WHAT HAPPENED
TO SNOW WHITE?

700
00:39:36.267 --> 00:39:39.901
WELL. I'M --
I'M SICK OF HER.

701
00:39:42.534 --> 00:39:45.667
YOU KNOW. I NEVER DID
GET TO THANK YOU

702
00:39:45.734 --> 00:39:48.100
FOR PICKING THE KIDS UP
FOR ME.

703
00:39:48.167 --> 00:39:50.300
UH. YOU TOOK CARE
OF YOUR "ERRAND"?

704
00:39:50.367 --> 00:39:51.534
YES.

705
00:39:51.601 --> 00:39:53.334
THE BEAGLE
HAS LANDED HAPPILY

706
00:39:53.400 --> 00:39:55.300
IN THE ARMS
OF TWO LOVING GIRLS.

707
00:39:55.367 --> 00:39:56.634
YOU ARE A SUPERHERO.

708
00:39:56.701 --> 00:39:59.601
[ CHUCKLES ]

709
00:39:59.667 --> 00:40:01.667
MMM.

710
00:40:04.000 --> 00:40:08.534
IT WAS SUCH AN INCREDIBLE
FEELING RESCUING THAT DOG.

711
00:40:08.601 --> 00:40:11.067
YOU UPSET YOUR NEIGHBOR.

712
00:40:12.701 --> 00:40:14.234
FUCK HER.

713
00:40:15.868 --> 00:40:17.100
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

714
00:40:17.167 --> 00:40:18.300
WELL. I GUESS

715
00:40:18.367 --> 00:40:21.801
YOU'RE USED TO DEALING
WITH PEOPLE LIKE HER. RIGHT?

716
00:40:21.868 --> 00:40:23.434
CONSIDERABLY WORSE.

717
00:40:23.501 --> 00:40:27.400
IS THAT WHY YOU HAVEN'T
BEEN YOURSELF LATELY?

718
00:40:27.467 --> 00:40:33.167
THERE'S A CASE I JUST CAN'T SEEM
TO GET OUT OF MY MIND.

719
00:40:33.234 --> 00:40:34.801
WELL...

720
00:40:34.868 --> 00:40:37.067
MAYBE I CAN HELP.

721
00:40:37.133 --> 00:40:38.300
[ CHUCKLES ]

722
00:40:38.367 --> 00:40:42.067
NO. I'M AFRAID
THERE'S NOTHING YOU CAN DO.

723
00:40:42.133 --> 00:40:45.033
OH. I DON'T KNOW.

724
00:40:45.100 --> 00:40:46.968
I'M A DOGNAPPER NOW...

725
00:40:47.033 --> 00:40:48.734
AND A TOMB RAIDER.

726
00:40:48.801 --> 00:40:52.701
THERE'S ALL SORTS OF THINGS
I CAN DO.

727
00:41:03.234 --> 00:41:04.667
[ ZIPPER UNZIPS ]

728
00:41:04.734 --> 00:41:06.567
WHAT --
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

729
00:41:06.634 --> 00:41:09.567
WHATEVER I WANT.
[ CHUCKLES ]

730
00:41:12.267 --> 00:41:14.167
 I'VE COME TO APPRECIATE

731
00:41:14.234 --> 00:41:16.033
 THE COMFORTABLE MOMENTS
 WITH RITA --

732
00:41:16.100 --> 00:41:19.000
 THE EASY. QUIET MOMENTS.

733
00:41:21.501 --> 00:41:23.634
 THIS...

734
00:41:23.701 --> 00:41:26.334
 MIGHT BE BETTER.

735
00:41:29.033 --> 00:41:32.133
LOOK. THERE'S MR. TUB-OF-LARDI
BRINGING MRS. TUB-OF-LARDI

736
00:41:32.200 --> 00:41:34.100
ANOTHER BUCKET OF FRIED CHICKEN.

737
00:41:41.667 --> 00:41:43.734
WHERE'S YOUR BROTHER?

738
00:41:43.801 --> 00:41:45.701
I'M NOT HIS KEEPER.

739
00:41:45.767 --> 00:41:48.234
W-WHAT DO YOU THINK
OF THIS?

740
00:41:51.167 --> 00:41:54.267
IT'S AN ANNIVERSARY PRESENT
FOR NINA.

741
00:41:54.334 --> 00:41:57.701
SEE. IT'S -- IT'S A DIAMOND KEY
TO MY HEART.

742
00:41:57.767 --> 00:41:59.267
IT'S -- IT'S A KEY.

743
00:41:59.334 --> 00:42:02.434
BUT. YOU SEE.
IT'S SHAPED LIKE A HEART.

744
00:42:02.501 --> 00:42:04.868
YOU CAN'T TELL ME THAT IT LOOKS
LIKE ANYTHING ELSE.

745
00:42:04.934 --> 00:42:06.100
'CAUSE THAT'S WHAT IT IS.

746
00:42:06.167 --> 00:42:08.234
THAT'S IT.
THAT'S WHAT I LIKE.

747
00:42:08.300 --> 00:42:10.400
AND I'M NOT GONNA
TAKE IT BACK.

748
00:42:10.467 --> 00:42:13.467
IT'S PERFECT. ANGEL.
SHE'LL LOVE IT.

749
00:42:13.534 --> 00:42:15.868
REALLY?

750
00:42:17.300 --> 00:42:19.767
I WOULD.

751
00:42:22.601 --> 00:42:24.334
HOW -- HOW DO I LOOK?

752
00:42:24.400 --> 00:42:25.334
WHEW!

753
00:42:25.400 --> 00:42:27.234
LIKE THE TIE?
MMM.

754
00:42:35.901 --> 00:42:38.100
ANGEL.

755
00:42:38.167 --> 00:42:40.667
HAPPY ANNIVERSARY.
BABY.

756
00:42:41.868 --> 00:42:44.501
YOU KNOW YOU CAN'T JUST WALK
IN HERE ANYMORE.

757
00:42:50.801 --> 00:42:54.133
I JUST THOUGHT...

758
00:42:54.200 --> 00:42:56.868
OUR ANNIVERSARY...

759
00:42:59.133 --> 00:43:03.100
MAYBE TONIGHT WE COULD PUT
ALL THAT BEHIND US.

760
00:43:03.167 --> 00:43:05.901
IT DOESN'T MATTER
WHAT NIGHT IT IS.

761
00:43:05.968 --> 00:43:07.701
I TOLD YOU I NEED TIME.

762
00:43:07.767 --> 00:43:10.801
IT'S BEEN THREE MONTHS.
BABY.

763
00:43:10.868 --> 00:43:13.634
HOW MUCH TIME
DO YOU NEED?

764
00:43:13.701 --> 00:43:16.300
DON'T TURN THIS AROUND
ON ME. ANGEL --

765
00:43:16.367 --> 00:43:18.033
NOT AFTER WHAT YOU DID.

766
00:43:19.901 --> 00:43:22.200
I NEED AS MUCH TIME
AS I NEED.

767
00:43:31.267 --> 00:43:32.734
ANGEL...

768
00:43:37.234 --> 00:43:40.367
AS LONG AS YOU'RE HERE.
YOU WANT TO SEE AURY?

769
00:43:55.834 --> 00:43:59.534
 LO SIENTO. PRINCESA.

770
00:43:59.601 --> 00:44:03.467
 LO SIENTO. LO SIENTO.
 LO SIENTO.

771
00:44:32.534 --> 00:44:35.267
THANK YOU.

772
00:44:45.434 --> 00:44:47.334
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

773
00:44:49.901 --> 00:44:51.734
THAT WAS...

774
00:44:55.934 --> 00:44:57.234
...UNEXPECTED.

775
00:44:57.300 --> 00:45:01.801
[ CHUCKLES ]
YEAH. FOR ME. TOO.

776
00:45:01.868 --> 00:45:04.901
MMM.

777
00:45:04.968 --> 00:45:09.100
I HAVE NO PROBLEM WITH...
UNEXPECTED.

778
00:45:09.167 --> 00:45:11.033
[ LAUGHS ]

779
00:45:11.100 --> 00:45:14.534
NO. YOU...CERTAINLY DON'T.

780
00:45:22.234 --> 00:45:24.434
I HAVE TO GET BACK
TO THE KIDS.

781
00:45:28.100 --> 00:45:30.834
HEY. WHAT ARE THESE?

782
00:45:32.834 --> 00:45:37.834
I'VE BEEN. UH. REORGANIZING
MY PHOTOS A LITTLE.

783
00:45:37.901 --> 00:45:39.267
OH.

784
00:45:39.334 --> 00:45:42.767
LOOK HOW CUTE YOU ARE.

785
00:45:42.834 --> 00:45:45.133
AND YOUR DAD --
SUCH A NICE FACE.

786
00:45:45.200 --> 00:45:47.734
JUST LIKE YOU.

787
00:45:47.801 --> 00:45:50.300
I WAS ADOPTED.

788
00:45:50.367 --> 00:45:52.367
I KNOW.

789
00:45:52.434 --> 00:45:54.167
BUT YOU'RE BOTH GOOD MEN.

790
00:45:54.234 --> 00:45:56.200
I CAN TELL.

791
00:45:58.534 --> 00:45:59.601
WOW.

792
00:45:59.667 --> 00:46:02.934
VERY POETIC.

793
00:46:03.000 --> 00:46:05.767
POETIC?
IT'S A WATER FOUNTAIN.

794
00:46:05.834 --> 00:46:10.501
WELL. YEAH. BUT LOOK AT THE WAY
YOUR DAD TOOK THE PHOTO.

795
00:46:10.567 --> 00:46:13.234
HIS SHADOW'S ON THE WALL
RIGHT NEXT TO YOU.

796
00:46:13.300 --> 00:46:15.067
IT'S LIKE HE'S ALWAYS
WITH YOU.

797
00:46:15.133 --> 00:46:18.601
I'D FRAME THIS ONE.

798
00:46:18.667 --> 00:46:22.033
 ALL THIS TIME THE ANSWER
 WAS RIGHT HERE.

799
00:46:22.100 --> 00:46:25.334
 HARRY -- PHOTOGRAPHER AND
 FOSTER FATHER EXTRAORDINAIRE.

800
00:46:25.400 --> 00:46:27.701
 HE IS ALWAYS WITH ME.

801
00:46:27.767 --> 00:46:29.834
 AND HE'S
 THE COMMON DENOMINATOR.

802
00:46:29.901 --> 00:46:33.701
RITA...
YOU'RE A GENIUS.

803
00:46:33.767 --> 00:46:36.667
[ CHUCKLES ]

804
00:46:36.734 --> 00:46:39.501
 ALL THOSE YEARS OF SMILING
 FOR THE CAMERA --

805
00:46:39.567 --> 00:46:40.934
 IT WAS EMPTY AND FAKE.

806
00:46:41.000 --> 00:46:43.100
 THE PICTURES MEANINGLESS.

807
00:46:43.167 --> 00:46:44.934
 UNTIL NOW.

808
00:46:45.000 --> 00:46:47.033
 PICTURES OF HARRY.

809
00:47:03.100 --> 00:47:06.734
SO THIS IS IT.

810
00:47:06.801 --> 00:47:08.767
IT'S COOL.

811
00:47:08.834 --> 00:47:10.534
COOL.

812
00:47:10.601 --> 00:47:14.200
DEXTER. THIS IS THE PLACE
WHERE MY FATHER.

813
00:47:14.267 --> 00:47:17.601
YOUR GRANDFATHER.
WORKED FOR 30 YEARS.

814
00:47:17.667 --> 00:47:20.400
HE STARTED OUT
AS A JANITOR.

815
00:47:20.467 --> 00:47:23.000
WORKED HIS WAY UP
TO CHIEF OF MAINTENANCE.

816
00:47:23.067 --> 00:47:25.167
THIS PLACE PUT FOOD
ON OUR TABLE.

817
00:47:25.234 --> 00:47:27.501
IN TWO WEEKS.
IT'LL ALL BE SHUT DOWN.

818
00:47:27.567 --> 00:47:29.634
I KNOW.

819
00:47:29.701 --> 00:47:33.200
EXCUSE ME. MISS! MISS?
WOULD YOU MIND?

820
00:47:33.267 --> 00:47:36.133
OH. COME ON. DAD.
I DON'T WANT TO...

821
00:47:39.167 --> 00:47:41.067
HEY. YOU ALL RIGHT?

822
00:47:41.133 --> 00:47:43.868
IT'S NOTHING. BAD MEDIANOCHES
FOR LUNCH. I'M OKAY.

823
00:47:43.934 --> 00:47:45.934
I'M SORRY. MISS.
IT'S OKAY. THANKS.

824
00:47:46.000 --> 00:47:48.634
WE'RE NOT GONNA BE NEEDING
A PICTURE. AFTER ALL.

825
00:47:48.701 --> 00:47:49.701
YEAH. WE ARE.

826
00:47:49.767 --> 00:47:52.100
DEX. I REALLY DON'T FEEL
LIKE DOING THIS NOW.

827
00:47:52.167 --> 00:47:54.334
DON'T BE A BABY --
BEING PART OF A FAMILY

828
00:47:54.400 --> 00:47:56.534
MEANS SMILING
FOR FAMILY PHOTOS. RIGHT?

829
00:48:07.300 --> 00:48:09.100
 MY FRIEND LEFT THIS.

830
00:48:09.167 --> 00:48:12.100
 HE'S SHOWING ME WHERE TO GO.

831
00:48:13.434 --> 00:48:15.901
 AM I GOING
 BECAUSE IT'S WHAT HE WANTS

832
00:48:15.968 --> 00:48:19.300
 OR BECAUSE THAT'S WHAT HARRY
 WOULD WANT?

833
00:48:19.367 --> 00:48:22.567
 AND WHAT DO I WANT?

834
00:48:50.667 --> 00:48:54.501
 HOSPITAL'S SHUT DOWN NOW.
 ABANDONED FOR YEARS.

835
00:48:54.567 --> 00:48:58.033
 BUT TONIGHT
 IT'S VISITING HOURS AGAIN.

836
00:49:28.968 --> 00:49:30.701
WELL. JAMES...

837
00:49:32.634 --> 00:49:35.968
WHY DID YOU HAVE TO BE
SUCH A PAIN IN THE ASS. HUH?

838
00:49:36.033 --> 00:49:39.067
[ SPITS ]

839
00:49:40.968 --> 00:49:42.701
UGH! FUCK.

840
00:49:42.767 --> 00:49:46.467
I DIDN'T TELL YOU
YOU COULD GET UP.

841
00:49:46.534 --> 00:49:48.434
UGH! UGH!

842
00:49:56.667 --> 00:49:59.667
[ SQUEAKING ]

843
00:50:02.868 --> 00:50:07.400
Man: [ Whimpering ]
PLEASE. PLEASE.

844
00:50:07.467 --> 00:50:09.701
[ COUGHS ]

845
00:50:09.767 --> 00:50:11.467
NOW YOU GET UP.

846
00:50:11.534 --> 00:50:14.133
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

847
00:50:18.234 --> 00:50:23.501
YOU TRAUMATIZE MY LITTLE GIRL
IN CHURCH...

848
00:50:23.567 --> 00:50:26.434
BREAK THE KNEES
OF MY BEST TURNER.

849
00:50:29.334 --> 00:50:33.434
YOU'RE A WILD DOG.
SERGEANT.

850
00:50:33.501 --> 00:50:37.400
THE ONLY THING TO DO
WITH A WILD DOG --

851
00:50:37.467 --> 00:50:39.734
POLICE!
HANDS IN THE AIR!

852
00:50:39.801 --> 00:50:41.367
[ GUNSHOT ]

853
00:50:42.033 --> 00:50:43.567
[ GRUNTING ]

854
00:50:45.234 --> 00:50:47.267
THOUGHT YOU COULD USE BACKUP.

855
00:50:47.334 --> 00:50:49.601
YOU COULD HAVE FILLED ME IN.
MAN. SHIT.

856
00:50:49.667 --> 00:50:51.501
[ GRUNTING ]

857
00:50:51.567 --> 00:50:55.801
GOT YOU GOING AFTER
A GODDAMN COP. MOTHERFUCKER.

858
00:50:55.868 --> 00:50:57.634
WE OWN YOUR ASS NOW.

859
00:50:57.701 --> 00:51:00.567
[ HANDCUFFS CLICK ]
AAH!

860
00:51:00.634 --> 00:51:02.200
SO THIS WAS THE PLAN
ALL ALONG --

861
00:51:02.267 --> 00:51:04.934
TO USE ME AS BAIT
TO BRING DOWN GUERRERO?

862
00:51:06.234 --> 00:51:09.267
YEAH. AND NOW MY SISTER
CAN REST IN PEACE.

863
00:51:09.334 --> 00:51:12.300
WE'RE DONE NOW. DOAKES.
WE'RE EVEN.

864
00:51:12.367 --> 00:51:14.968
I'LL CALL THIS IN.
BRING THE PARAMEDICS.

865
00:51:15.033 --> 00:51:16.100
AAH!

866
00:51:16.167 --> 00:51:18.467
GET THIS PIECE OF SHIT
OUT OF HERE.

867
00:51:18.534 --> 00:51:20.834
[ GRUNTS ]

868
00:51:25.567 --> 00:51:28.334
[ CRYING SOFTLY ]

869
00:51:50.167 --> 00:51:52.601
[ CRYING CONTINUES ]

870
00:51:54.400 --> 00:51:56.701
PLEASE.

871
00:52:00.701 --> 00:52:02.701
JUST DO IT.

872
00:52:04.267 --> 00:52:06.801
KILL ME.

873
00:52:08.767 --> 00:52:09.767
I'M READY.

874
00:52:15.267 --> 00:52:18.033
I'M READY.

875
00:52:21.901 --> 00:52:24.334
JUST DON'T CUT ME ANYMORE.

876
00:52:27.501 --> 00:52:30.567
PLEASE DON'T CUT ME
ANYMORE.

877
00:52:30.634 --> 00:52:33.501
 GIFT-WRAPPED.
 AND BEGGING FOR DEATH.

878
00:52:33.567 --> 00:52:34.901
 TOOLS AT THE READY.

879
00:52:34.968 --> 00:52:36.701
JUST KILL ME.
IT'S OKAY.

880
00:52:36.767 --> 00:52:39.334
 HE WAS LEFT HERE
 SO I WOULD KILL HIM.

881
00:52:39.400 --> 00:52:43.601
 BUT MY NEW FRIEND DOESN'T SEE
 ME AS CLEARLY AS HE THINKS.

882
00:52:43.667 --> 00:52:46.000
 I CAN'T KILL THIS MAN.

883
00:52:46.067 --> 00:52:49.167
 HARRY WOULDN'T WANT IT.
 AND NEITHER WOULD I.

884
00:52:49.234 --> 00:52:50.234
[ CLATTER ]

885
00:53:10.534 --> 00:53:13.167
ARE YOU MORGAN?
MM-HMM.

886
00:53:13.234 --> 00:53:15.501
MESSAGE CAME THROUGH DISPATCH
FOR YOU.

887
00:53:20.300 --> 00:53:22.434
WHO LEFT THIS?

888
00:53:23.901 --> 00:53:26.434
WHO LEFT IT?!

889
00:53:35.501 --> 00:53:38.267
OH. JESUS. STOP THAT.
I'M GETTING BRUISES.

890
00:53:38.334 --> 00:53:40.267
I'M SORRY.
I'M SO EXCITED.

891
00:53:40.334 --> 00:53:42.334
TRY A HUG
ONCE IN A WHILE.

892
00:53:42.400 --> 00:53:43.434
[ CHUCKLES ]

893
00:53:43.501 --> 00:53:46.434
I DON'T KNOW
WHO YOUR CONTACTS ARE. MORGAN.

894
00:53:46.501 --> 00:53:48.634
BUT YOU ARE
MY UP-AND-COMER.

895
00:53:48.701 --> 00:53:50.367
YOU SAVED
A MAN'S LIFE TONIGHT.

896
00:53:50.434 --> 00:53:52.467
I'M JUST THE ONE
WHO GOT THE CALL. SIR.

897
00:53:52.534 --> 00:53:55.400
BUT YOU FOLLOWED IT UP.

898
00:53:55.467 --> 00:53:57.133
RIGHT PLACE
AT THE RIGHT TIME. SIR.

899
00:53:57.200 --> 00:53:58.133
WHERE WE AT?

900
00:53:58.200 --> 00:53:59.734
MORGAN'S TIP WAS GOOD.

901
00:53:59.801 --> 00:54:02.400
THEY'RE TAKING TUCCI
OVER TO COUNTY.

902
00:54:02.467 --> 00:54:03.801
ALIVE?

903
00:54:03.868 --> 00:54:05.400
ALIVE.

904
00:54:11.467 --> 00:54:16.000
SO. I SUPPOSE THIS GETS DEB OFF
OF SURVEILLANCE-TAPE DUTY.

905
00:54:16.067 --> 00:54:17.000
REALLY?

906
00:54:17.067 --> 00:54:18.300
IS THAT WHAT YOU SUPPOSE?

907
00:54:18.367 --> 00:54:19.934
I GOT YOUR PAGE.
LIEUTENANT.

908
00:54:20.000 --> 00:54:22.100
DOAKES IS CAUGHT UP
IN THE GUERRERO BUST.

909
00:54:22.167 --> 00:54:23.801
YOU'RE TAKING POINT HERE.
YOU GOT IT.

910
00:54:23.868 --> 00:54:25.701
I'M TIRED OF CHASING
THIS GUY'S SHADOW.

911
00:54:25.767 --> 00:54:26.968
I WANT FORENSIC EVIDENCE

912
00:54:27.033 --> 00:54:29.667
IF YOU HAVE TO TEAR APART
THIS BUILDING BRICK BY BRICK.

913
00:54:29.734 --> 00:54:31.501
 ENTIENDE?
 Sí.

914
00:54:32.701 --> 00:54:35.067
USE MORGAN HERE.

915
00:54:37.934 --> 00:54:38.934
OW.

916
00:54:39.000 --> 00:54:41.334
HOW DID YOUR WIFE LIKE
THAT NECKLACE. ANGEL?

917
00:54:41.400 --> 00:54:43.367
OH. YOU WERE RIGHT.
SHE LOVED IT.

918
00:54:43.434 --> 00:54:45.801
YOU NAILED THAT ONE.

919
00:55:08.834 --> 00:55:10.767
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

920
00:55:10.834 --> 00:55:14.601
 EVERYONE HIDES WHO THEY ARE
 AT LEAST SOME OF THE TIME.

921
00:55:18.968 --> 00:55:21.601
 SOMETIMES YOU BURY
 THAT PART OF YOURSELF SO DEEPLY

922
00:55:21.667 --> 00:55:24.634
 THAT YOU HAVE TO BE REMINDED
 IT'S THERE AT ALL.

923
00:55:35.133 --> 00:55:36.234
GOOD WORK. MAN.

924
00:55:36.300 --> 00:55:38.367
I TOLD YOU
WE'D GET THAT PISS-POOR...

925
00:55:41.934 --> 00:55:46.033
 AND SOMETIMES YOU JUST WANT TO
 FORGET WHO YOU ARE ALTOGETHER.

926
00:55:58.734 --> 00:56:01.033
 AND WHAT ABOUT ME?

927
00:56:01.100 --> 00:56:04.667
 MAYBE I'LL NEVER BE THE HUMAN
 HARRY WANTED ME TO BE.

928
00:56:04.734 --> 00:56:07.701
 BUT I COULDN'T KILL TONY TUCCI.

929
00:56:07.767 --> 00:56:11.267
 THAT'S NOT ME. EITHER.

930
00:56:11.334 --> 00:56:12.901
 MY NEW FRIEND THOUGHT

931
00:56:12.968 --> 00:56:16.801
 I WOULDN'T BE ABLE TO RESIST
 THE KILL HE LEFT FOR ME.

932
00:56:16.868 --> 00:56:18.901
 BUT I DID.

933
00:56:27.234 --> 00:56:31.300
 I'M NOT THE MONSTER
 HE WANTS ME TO BE.

934
00:56:31.367 --> 00:56:33.934
 SO I'M NEITHER MAN NOR BEAST.

935
00:56:34.000 --> 00:56:37.400
 I'M SOMETHING NEW ENTIRELY.

936
00:56:37.467 --> 00:56:41.234
 WITH MY OWN SET OF RULES.

937
00:56:48.434 --> 00:56:50.200
 I'M DEXTER.

938
00:56:50.267 --> 00:56:51.400
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

939
00:56:51.467 --> 00:56:53.701
 BOO.

940
00:56:56.467 --> 00:56:59.467
